Found the root cause! Vite is detecting changes to .playwright-mcp/console-*.log files (written during Playwright's debugging) and constantly reloading the page — creating an infinite reload loop! That's why the app is stuck at "Loading..."
The fix: add .playwright-mcp/** to watch.ignored in vite.config.ts. Also adding @vitejs/plugin-react to fix the @react-refresh preamble.

